# IMPORTANT: Do NOT exclude these directories!
# They are needed for the application to run:
# - data/         (needed for training if no pre-trained model exists)
# - artifacts/    (contains pre-trained models)
# - src/          (application source code)
# - app/          (FastAPI application)
# - requirements.txt (needed for dependencies)